sentence.Network_en: The paper proposes a nonmonotonic BFGS - trust - region algorithm for unconstrained optimization.
sentence.Network_cn: 给出了一个解无约束最优化问题的非单调的新的BFGS校正的信赖域算法.

sentence.Network_en: A nonmonotonic criterion is also used to speed up the convergence.
sentence.Network_cn: 同时算法采用非单调的技术来加速算法的收敛效果.

sentence.Network_en: In the third chapter, nonmonotonic trust region algorithms for nonlinear constrained optimization are discussed.
sentence.Network_cn: 第三章讨论了非线性约束优化的非单调信赖域算法.
